      m_Body: "A bit of awkwardness....\n\nAt runtime, we only want ONE of these prefabs active.\nWe have two things to check; \n-Whether it is a new save (or an old one), and\n-Whether IAPs are available (The downloaded GameConfig will contain a flag)\n\nWe show an IAP warning dialog iff a new save AND IAPs are available.\n\n(Note; It was done this way since it carries less risk to choose which one fully-fledged instance to make active rather than monkey about with a single one)\n"
      m_LastEditUsername: swoollard
